title: 05/27/21 DPS Hour 2 Trevor Lawrence
itunes:title: 05/27/21 DPS Hour 2 Trevor Lawrence
description:
Trevor Lawrence tells Dan that it was hard to learn and remember all the names on his new team. Trevor says that basketball was his second best sport and that he really loves to play for fun. And he talks about practicing with Tim Tebow.
